while trying to compile su.c, I got the following error:

su.c: In function `main':
su.c:402: `lc' undeclared (first use this function)

Fix: 

here is the diff of su.c:

@@ -399,7 +399,9 @@
                 syslog(LOG_NOTICE|LOG_AUTH, "%s to %s%s",
                     username, user, ontty());

+#ifdef LOGIN_CAP
         login_close(lc);
+#endif

         execv(shell, np);
         err(1, "%s", shell);
